sqls.name: TasksByUser
sqls.sql:
SELECT id, type, priority, service_id, activity, creationdate, workitem_id, 
       flowelement_id, task, currentgroup_id, currentgroup, responsible_id, 
       responsible, responsible_login, statusid, flowstatus, flowstatus_id, 
       backgroundcolor, textcolor, slalimit, workitem_status, requester, 
       contact_dept_id, contact_dept, contact_phone, contact_email, 
       locality_id, location, contract_id, contract_number, impact, 
       urgency, deadline_hh, deadline_mm, pasttime_hh, pasttime_mm, 
       response, relatedrequest_id, configurationitem   FROM vw_itsm_tasks
    WHERE workitem_status IN (1, 2) 
    AND statusid NOT IN (5, 7)
 AND responsible_login = ${username}  ORDER BY  DESC

       backgroundcolor, textcolor, slalimit, workitem_status, requester, 
       contact_dept_id, contact_dept, contact_phone, contact_email, 
       locality_id, location, contract_id, contract_number, impact, 
       urgency, deadline_hh, deadline_mm, pasttime_hh, pasttime_mm, 
       response, relatedrequest_id, configurationitem
sqls.fromWhereQueryPiece:
FROM vw_itsm_tasks
    WHERE workitem_status IN (1, 2) 
    AND statusid NOT IN (5, 7)
 AND responsible_login = ${username}

sqls.name: TasksByUserGroups
sqls.sql:
SELECT id, type, priority, service_id, activity, creationdate, workitem_id, 
       flowelement_id, task, currentgroup_id, currentgroup, responsible_id, 
       responsible, responsible_login, statusid, flowstatus, flowstatus_id, 
       backgroundcolor, textcolor, slalimit, workitem_status, requester, 
       contact_dept_id, contact_dept, contact_phone, contact_email, 
       locality_id, location, contract_id, contract_number, impact, 
       urgency, deadline_hh, deadline_mm, pasttime_hh, pasttime_mm, 
       response, relatedrequest_id, configurationitem FROM vw_itsm_tasks
WHERE     workitem_status IN (1, 2, 3) 
    AND statusid NOT IN (5, 7) 
    AND 0 < (select count(*) from bpm_atribuicaofluxo where iditemtrabalho = workitem_id 
   and idtype = 1 and idgrupo in (select idgrupo from gruposempregados ge inner join usuario usu on usu .idempregado = ge.idempregado 
   where usu.login = ${username} and usu.status = 'A')) ORDER BY workitem_id DESC

       flowelement_id, task, currentgroup_id, currentgroup, responsible_id, 
       responsible, responsible_login, statusid, flowstatus, flowstatus_id, 
       backgroundcolor, textcolor, slalimit, workitem_status, requester, 
       contact_dept_id, contact_dept, contact_phone, contact_email, 
       locality_id, location, contract_id, contract_number, impact, 
       urgency, deadline_hh, deadline_mm, pasttime_hh, pasttime_mm, 
       response, relatedrequest_id, configurationitem from  vw_itsm_tasks
    WHERE workitem_status in (1,2) 
    AND statusid NOT IN (5, 7) 
    AND responsible IS NULL
    AND ((0 < (select count(*) from bpm_atribuicaofluxo where iditemtrabalho = workitem_id 
   and idtype = 1 and idgrupo in (select idgrupo from gruposempregados ge inner join usuario usu on usu.idempregado = ge.idempregado 
   where usu.login = ${username} and usu.status = 'A'))
  OR 0 < (select count(*) from bpm_atribuicaofluxo inner join usuario usu on usu.idusuario = bpm_atribuicaofluxo.idusuario
    where iditemtrabalho = workitem_id and idtype = 1 and usu.login = ${username}))) ORDER BY workitem_id DESC

sqls.name: ChangeRequestsByUserGroups
sqls.sql:
SELECT t.id, type, priority, service_id, activity, creationdate, workitem_id, 
       flowelement_id, task, currentgroup_id, currentgroup, responsible_id, 
       responsible, responsible_login, statusid, flowstatus, flowstatus_id, 
       backgroundcolor, textcolor, slalimit, workitem_status, requester, 
       contact_dept_id, contact_dept, contact_phone, contact_email, 
       locality_id, location, contract_id, contract_number, impact, 
       urgency, deadline_hh, deadline_mm, pasttime_hh, pasttime_mm, 
       response, relatedrequest_id, configurationitem, s.name || ' - ' || 
       case when cr.scheduling = 1 then 'Imediata' when cr.scheduling = 2 then 'Fora do expediente' when cr.scheduling = 3 then 'Agendada para ' || to_char(cr.schedulingdate, 'dd/MM/yyyy') || ' às ' || substr(cr.schedulinghour, 1, 2) || ':' || substr(cr.schedulinghour, 3, 2) end as "details"
 FROM vw_itsm_tasks t inner join cr_changerequest cr on cr.itsm_id = cast(t.id as number)  
inner join cr_systemcatalog s on s.id = cr.system_id    
WHERE 0 < (select count(*) from bpm_atribuicaofluxo where iditemtrabalho = workitem_id 
   and idtype = 1 and idgrupo in (select idgrupo from gruposempregados ge inner join usuario usu on usu .idempregado = ge.idempregado 
   where usu.login = ${username} and usu.status = 'A')) ORDER BY workitem_id DESC

dataObjects.ddl:
CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW vw_itsm_tasks as 
 SELECT cast(r.idsolicitacaoservico as varchar) as id,
        CASE
            WHEN r.idtipodemandaservico = 1 THEN 'R'
            WHEN r.idtipodemandaservico = 3 THEN 'I'
        END AS type,
    r.idprioridade AS priority,
    s.idservico AS service_id,
    s.nomeservico AS activity,
    r.datahorasolicitacao AS creationdate,
    i.iditemtrabalho AS workitem_id,
    e.idelemento AS flowelement_id,
    e.nome AS task,
    g.idgrupo AS currentgroup_id,
    g.nome AS currentgroup,
    u.idusuario AS responsible_id,
    u.nome AS responsible,
    u.login AS responsible_login,
    r.idstatus AS statusid,
        CASE
            WHEN st.expressionid IS NULL AND r.idstatus = 1 THEN 'citcorpore.comum.emandamento'
            WHEN st.expressionid IS NULL AND r.idstatus = 2 THEN 'citcorpore.comum.suspensa'
            WHEN st.expressionid IS NULL AND r.idstatus = 4 THEN 'citcorpore.comum.resolvida'
            WHEN st.expressionid IS NULL AND r.idstatus = 5 THEN 'citcorpore.comum.reaberta'
            WHEN st.expressionid IS NULL AND r.idstatus = 7 THEN 'citcorpore.comum.reclassificada'
            WHEN st.expressionid IS NOT NULL THEN st.description
        END AS flowstatus,
    st.expressionid AS flowstatus_id,
    st.backgroundcolor,
    st.textcolor,
    r.datahoralimite AS slalimit,
    i.idstatus AS workitem_status,
    employee.nome as requester,
    un.idunidade as contact_dept_id,  	
    un.nome as contact_dept,  
    cs.telefonecontato as contact_phone,  	
    cs.emailcontato as contact_email, 
    cs.idlocalidade as locality_id,  	
    cs.localizacaofisica as location,
    c.idcontrato as contract_id, 	
    c.numero as contract_number,
    r.impacto as impact,  	
    r.urgencia as urgency,	
    r.prazohh as deadline_hh, 	
    r.prazomm as deadline_mm, 	
    r.tempodecorridohh as pasttime_hh, 	
    r.tempodecorridomm as pasttime_mm,
    r.resposta as response,
    r.idsolicitacaorelacionada as relatedrequest_id,
    (select top 1 ci.identificacao 
      from itemconfiguracao ci inner join itemcfgsolicitacaoserv icr on icr.iditemconfiguracao = ci.iditemconfiguracao  where icr.idsolicitacaoservico = r.idsolicitacaoservico) as configurationitem
 FROM solicitacaoservico r
     JOIN servicocontrato sc ON sc.idservicocontrato = r.idservicocontrato
     JOIN servico s ON s.idservico = sc.idservico
     JOIN execucaosolicitacao ex ON ex.idsolicitacaoservico = r.idsolicitacaoservico
     JOIN bpm_instanciafluxo inst ON inst.idinstancia = ex.idinstanciafluxo
     JOIN bpm_itemtrabalhofluxo i ON i.idinstancia = ex.idinstanciafluxo
     JOIN bpm_elementofluxo e ON e.idelemento = i.idelemento
     left join empregados employee               on employee.idempregado = r.idsolicitante
      left join unidade un              on un.idunidade = r.idunidade  
       left join contatosolicitacaoservico cs               on cs.idcontatosolicitacaoservico =                  r.idcontatosolicitacaoservico  
       left join contratos c               on c.idcontrato = sc.idcontrato
     LEFT JOIN grupo g ON g.idgrupo = r.idgrupoatual
     LEFT JOIN usuario u ON u.idusuario = i.idresponsavelatual
     LEFT JOIN bpm_expression st ON st.expressionid = inst.idstatusfluxo
